{"title":"(19) implementacion-amb-sysmayal2 - Raven","url":"https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-implementacion-amb-sysmayal2","summary":"This is a Raven chat channel for AMB-Wellsness implementation tracking. The page contains a conversation between administrators discussing the Manufacturing AI Agent (ravens @ai commands) for an ERPNext system. The chat shows various @ai commands being tested and their responses, including deployment fixes for bugs in the manufacturing agent system. Key issues discussed include work order creation, work order planning from sales orders, and item code parsing fixes.","key_points":["@ai show work orders - Returns a table of active work orders with details including Work Order, Product, Qty, Transferred, Status, and SO","@ai create work order for [ITEM] qty [QTY] - Creates a new work order in draft status","@manufacturing create wo for [ITEM] qty [QTY] - Manufacturing Agent command to create WO from default BOM","@manufacturing create wo for [ITEM] qty [QTY] bom [BOM-NAME] - Create WO with specific BOM","@manufacturing create wo from so [SO-NAME] - Create WO linked to Sales Order","@manufacturing submit wo [WO-NAME] - Submit Work Order","@manufacturing transfer materials [WO-NAME] - Transfer materials to WIP","@manufacturing manufacture [WO-NAME] - Create Stock Entry (Manufacture)","@manufacturing status [WO-NAME] - Detailed WO status with linked docs","@manufacturing check materials [WO-NAME] - Verify material availability","Deployment fixes applied: GAP-02 (resolve_bom variant template fallback), GAP-03 (create_wo_plan multi-WO split), GAP-04 (create_named_batch), ARCH-03 (show_work_orders routing)","Bug fix: Item code regex updated from (\\S+) to (.+?)(?:\\s+qty\\b|\\s+bom\\b|\\s+from\\b|$) to handle item codes with spaces","Successfully created work orders: MFG-WO-05126, MFG-WO-05226 for item 0803- KOSHER-ORGANIC-LAS3-HADS NMT 2 PPM-ACM 15/20","Work orders listed include various statuses: Completed, Not Started, Draft","Sales Order SO-00763-LORAND LABORATORIES is being used for work order planning tests"],"relevant_links":["https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-05026","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-05126","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/work-order/MFG-WO-05226","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/bom/BOM-0803- KOSHER-ORGANIC-LAS3-HADS NMT 2 PPM-ACM 15/20-002"],"file_name":"raven_ai_commands_work_orders.json"}
